A4.text: A Whiter Shade of Pale is a song by Procol Harum

A5.text: In April 1967 the group entered Olympic Studios in London to record their debut single, 'A Whiter Shade of Pale'

A6.text: Procol Harum played their first live gig at London's Speakeasy club on the day 'A Whiter Shade of Pale' was released on 12 May 1967
